title: Muddy Waters Band feat. B.B. King - Live At Ebbets Field (2015)
description:
The Muddy Waters Blues Band feat. B.B. King - Live At Ebbets Field
Label: Klondike - KLCD5025
Format: CD, Album, Reissue, Remastered
Released: 2015
Recorded May 30, 1973 at Ebbets Field, Denver, CO
Genre: Blues


Tracklist:

1 	Piano Jam
2 	Instrumental (Hideaway)
3 	Instrumental with Muddy Intro
4 	My Sweet Little Baby
5 	Rock Me
6 	Can't Get No Grindin'
7 	I've Got My Mojo Working
8 	Forty Days and Forty Nights
9 	Band Introductions
10 	I Know You Didn't Want Me
11 	The Thrill Is Gone
12 	Instrumental
13 	Caldonia 


Lineup:

Muddy Waters - vocals, guitar
Hollywood Fats - guitar
Pinetop Perkins - piano (tracks 1-8)
Calvin 'Fuzz' Jones - bass
Willie 'Big Eye' Smith - drums

B.B. King - guitar, vocals (tracks 10-13)
Kato - piano (tracks 10-13)
